6Ô∏è‚É£ Spring vs Spring Boot
Definition
Spring Boot is an opinionated framework built on top of Spring to simplify configuration and deployment.

Key Points
No XML configuration
Embedded servers (Tomcat)
Auto configuration
Faster development

7Ô∏è‚É£ Spring Boot Architecture
Definition
Architecture that enables auto-configured, standalone Spring applications.

Key Points
@SpringBootApplication
Auto Configuration
Starter Dependencies
